				"body": <<<"
					<p>By creating a sense of danger, such as threatening account suspension, work or financial consequences, they prompt hasty actions like sharing passwords or revealing details. </p>

					<p>Verify the legitimacy of these threats or consequences by contacting the entity directly through known, official channels, checking correct procedures before taking any action.</p>
