				"body": <<<"
					<p>Promising lucrative rewards, they entice the sharing of financial or personal details. They may also be combined with urgency, urging you to act now or lose out on an opportunity or deal.</p>  

					<p>Be skeptical of offers that seem too good to be true. Research the offer and the entity providing it before sharing any information. Evaluate whether the value is worth the risk.</p>
